name: Tetris
description: Welcome to the Tetris token, where you can battle it out in head to head competitions, defeat the competition and win crypto! Challenge your friends, enemies or strangers to the ultimate retro game! Feel the thrill of winning eth, the agony of defeat and the satisfaction of revenge! Tetris Eth will add another level to the worlds most popular retro game! Tetris Eth will provide a wallet connect dapp where participants will be able to stake their eth in PVP tournaments, place bets on active tournaments and participate in Tetris Eth's tournaments where winners will be paid out in eth.
